  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我想画一个简化版的前端架构流程图，核心是从用户操作到数据层的流向。最左边是User，中间经过UI层，然后是Logic逻辑层，最后落到Data数据层。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "UI",
        "Logic",
        "Data"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，是一个TD（从上到下）的流向。确认一下连接关系：User指向UI，UI指向Logic，Logic再指向Data，对吗？没有其他分支或循环？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "UI",
        "Logic",
        "Data"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就是单向的调用链。User通过UI发起操作，UI把请求交给Logic处理，Logic最后去读写Data。保持简单，不用画返回箭头。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "UI",
        "Logic",
        "Data"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经创建了四个节点，按垂直方向排列：顶部是User，往下依次是UI、Logic、Data。连线也画好了，都是单向箭头。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "UI",
        "Logic",
        "Data"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，我看了一眼，Logic到Data的箭头方向是不是反了？应该是Logic去调用Data，不是Data调用Logic。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logic",
        "Data"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "抱歉，是我搞错了。现在修正：Logic指向下方的Data，箭头从Logic出发指向Data，方向已经调过来了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logic",
        "Data"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "现在对了。整个链条是User→UI→Logic→Data，符合我们讨论的调用顺序。这个图可以定稿了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "UI",
        "Logic",
        "Data"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认定稿。最终结构：User连接UI，UI连接Logic，Logic连接Data，单向垂直流向，无其他元素。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "UI",
        "Logic",
        "Data"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
